{"tid":1703972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北辰：專家小組進展報告為獨立調查修例風波下台階","createTime":"2019-11-10T13:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T13:47:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5272b6d5f961b10d8c21ec02fd1072b3be627615","tid":1703972,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"監警會早前邀請的海外專家Clifford Stott，在社交網站發佈專家小組的《進展報告》，指監警會缺乏權力及獨立調查能力，認為監警會完成初步報告後，可以讓另一個有權力而獨立的機構，進行更深入全面調查。實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰指，專家小組有成員亦認為調查元朗襲擊事件和太子站事件有困難，因為涉及敏感資料，舉證有難度，他認為，專家小組的進展報告可以成為政府的下台階，建議當局表明在監警會提交中期報告後，成立獨立調查委員會，跟進修例風波的多個問題，包括警方使用武力情況、政府在風波的角色、示威者的背景等，相信可以回應大部份人的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1207571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1207571&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=a10e16c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1207571</a>"},{"pid":"323d8781ef0c1e65707b548e5a0b1ac28643c016","tid":1703972,"uid":44870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"7f2ecc3f5fe1fdc4549f58668e2ff43ec3d3f04e","tid":1703972,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我要番工 千祈唔好咁做!!!!!!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MG7Hx4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMG7Hx4n.png&h=41866d85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGwhmXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGwhmXJ.png&h=8e8bb265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(科普)作為一個工程佬等我話比你知黨鐵最煩既設備係咩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594466\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla